{"title":"“颂毒文学”","authors":["天马","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“颂毒文学”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马　诗  方成　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：在美国出现了一种颂扬毒品的“文学”，把毒品看作是“灵感的源泉”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“作家”灵感何处寻？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白面、鸦片、海洛因！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源源不绝取不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒品之中出“作品”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"异想天开好“聪明”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老板一见喜盈盈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正愁愚民无妙计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送来宝贝胜黄金！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云里来呀雾里去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人若乐此他放心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒品“作品”大拍卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双毒齐下功夫深！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普天之下谁“文明”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要数美国是冠军！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒品毒虫和毒气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟它难舍又难分！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}